  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1000">
<l>paṇpilāṉ peṟṟa peruñcelva naṉpāl</l>
<l>kalantīmai yāṟṟirin taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great wealth obtained by one who has no goodness will perish like pure milk spoilt by the impurity of the vessel.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
